| Parameter | Value | Notes |
|-----------|-------|-------|
| **Order type** | `LimitIncrease` | Created automatically when `limitPrice` is set |
| **Trigger condition** | Oracle price **≤ $2,800** | Long limits buy the dip |
| **Pay amount** | 100 USDC | Adjust `PAY_AMOUNT_USDC` to your desired size |
